# Cross-origin isolation headers required for SharedArrayBuffer.
#
# SharedArrayBuffer is gated behind cross-origin isolation in all modern
# browsers. Without both headers below, Emscripten pthreads (audio worker,
# async asset loading) will throw at runtime.
#
# This file is consumed unchanged by both Cloudflare Pages and Netlify.
# Drop it at the root of the published directory alongside the built WASM
# artifacts and the host will inject these headers on every response.

/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin
